{
  "title": "Iced Springy Dutch Cabbage Salad",
  "description": "A crunchy, cool salad that captures Dutch nostalgia with a zing of English mustard and an ice-bath shock, perfect for a light, ayurvedic-rajasic friendly meal.",
  "cuisine": "Dutch",
