  "instructions": [
    "Rinse the cabbage in cold water and slice thinly.",
    "Place the sliced cabbage in a large bowl and pour ice water over it; let it sit for 10 minutes to cool and soften.",
    "Drain the cabbage, reserving 1 cup of the ice water for the dressing.",
    "Whisk together mustard, vinegar, honey, olive oil, salt, pepper, and a splash of the reserved ice water until smooth.",
    "Toss the cabbage, carrot, raisins, dill, and almonds with the dressing until evenly coated.",
    "Let the salad rest for 15 minutes at room temperature to allow flavors to mingle.",
    "Before serving, chill the salad in the refrigerator for 20 minutes and then bring it to room temperature.",
    "Serve scooped in bowls, garnished with extra dill."
  ],
